        "content": "<h3>Magento is one of the most popular ecommerce platforms in the world, and attracts businesses of all sizes and industry focus. Though Magento markets itself as the perfect solution, it can be frustrating for a new user without coding or web development experience to manage. The advantages of using Magento include the opportunity to create a fully customizable web store if your coding knowledge gives you the ability to use its robust open source framework. If you are a small business owner searching for a simpler solution or do not want to hire an IT manager, you might want to check out some of the best Magento competitors that are currently available in the world of B2B ecommerce. There are certainly some great alternatives to Magento to explore as the ecommerce landscape is rapidly changing.&nbsp;</h3>\n",
