                "title": "Closed or Open Source",
                "text": "<p>Open source software like Linux or Mozilla Web Browser and closed source or so-called proprietary software, like Microsoft Windows or Adobe products, have been around for a long time. Open source platforms offer a high level of customizability while at the same time being almost entirely free. However, there are certain things that they lack that closed source platforms have. If you prefer to have full control over your website, share extensions and plug-ins with the community, then open source Magento alternatives will be the way to go for you.</p>\n"
            },
            {
