                    "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/payment.png"
                },
                "title": "Total Cost of Ownership",
                "text": "<p>Proprietary (closed source) platforms come with a price tag that can add up. At the same time, open source Magento competitors offer basic features for free. However, if you would like to get an enterprise package or develop your website&#39;s functionality with extensions, the bills will run up.</p>\n"
