                "title": "Special Features",
                "text": "<p>Always try to look for Magento competitors that have lots of extensions and plugins to work with. The right platform is the one that will help you uncover your website&#39;s potential and broaden its functionality.</p>\n"
            },
            {
                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vc4test.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/architect.png"
